            <h2 class="lead">II. Rural Communities</h2>
            <h3>1. Small towns are rural communities</h3>
            <p>Small towns are in the contryside. They are far from cities. Small towns have fewer people than cities. Everybody knows their neightbors in a small town. Smalll towns might have just on store. There maybe a post office, bank and a school.</p>
            <h3>2. Living in Rural communities</h3>
            <p>Many people live and work on farms in rural communities. They drive to the store and the post office. Kids walk by foot when they go to school. There are different ways to have fun in a small town. In a city, you might visit a big aquarium. In a small town, you might go fishing. What would you do in small town.</p>
